<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انْشَقَّتْ <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَإِذَا الْأَرْضُ مُدَّتْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَأَلْقَتْ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتْ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>